---
// ParentFAQ.astro — short parent-facing FAQ, landing page placement
---

<section class="section" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
  <p class="section-label">For Parents</p>
  <h2 class="section-title" id="faq-heading">Questions we hear first.</h2>

  <dl class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <dt>Is this tackle rugby?</dt>
      <dd>No. The first youth offering is non-contact tag rugby. There will be no tackling, scrums, rucks, mauls, or contact drills.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <dt>What is tag rugby?</dt>
      <dd>Tag rugby is a non-contact version of rugby. Players wear tags or flags, and defenders stop play by pulling a tag instead of tackling.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <dt>What age groups is this for?</dt>
      <dd>The first focus is elementary and middle school students. Exact age and grade groups will depend on interest, volunteer support, field access, and registration requirements.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <dt>Does my child need experience?</dt>
      <dd>No. The program is designed for beginners.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <dt>Do parents need to volunteer?</dt>
      <dd>Parent help will be important. No rugby experience is required for many volunteer roles.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-list {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 61, 46, 0.12);
    padding: 28px 0;
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 61, 46, 0.12);
  }

  dt {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
